<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>vCard — Digitala NFC-visitkort</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="home-page">
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect x="1" y="4" width="20" height="14" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/>
        <circle cx="7.5" cy="10" r="2.2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"/>
        <line x1="12" y1="8.5" x2="18" y2="8.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <line x1="12" y1="11.5" x2="16" y2="11.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      vCard
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard">Min profil</a>
        <% if (user.is_admin) { %><a href="/admin">Admin</a><% } %>
        <a href="/auth/logout">Logga ut</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 7px 16px; font-size: 13px;">Logga in</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="home">
    <div class="home-badge">NFC-visitkort · Sverige</div>
    <h1>Ditt kort.<br>Alltid aktuellt.</h1>
    <p>Håll kortet mot en telefon — kontakten sparas direkt.<br>Uppdatera din info när som helst utan att byta kort.</p>
    <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary home-cta">Kom igång</a>

    <div class="home-features">
      <div class="home-feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">📲</span>
        <strong>En tapp räcker</strong>
        <span>Fungerar med alla moderna telefoner, ingen app krävs.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">✏️</span>
        <strong>Redigera när som helst</strong>
        <span>Byt telefonnummer eller titel — kortet uppdateras omedelbart.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">🇸🇪</span>
        <strong>Hostad i Sverige</strong>
        <span>All data lagras på svenska servrar. GDPR-säkert.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="home-footer">
    <span>© 2026 vCard</span>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
